// Modeling result selection.
// If there is only one modeling object, then there is nothing to
// select. In that case, only the modeling info button is displayed.
// Otherwise, a modeling selection form is displayed.
div(ng-switch="modelings.length")
  div(*ngSwitchCase="1")
    // The repeat below only serves to place the modeling object in
    // scope for the modeling info modal pop-up. The repeat block
    // includes the title in order to display the button on the same
    // line as the title.
    .qi-left-space.qi-bottom-space(*ngFor="let modeling in modelings")
      span.qi-title.qi-inset Modeling Input Parameters:
      include modeling-info-btn
